window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As a private investigator, I get my fair share of crazy clients. But when an attractive college girl comes to me, telling me her best friend had been taken by fairies, I want to believe she's telling the truth.</p> <p>Turns out, she is.</p> <p>Tracking down her friend leads me to a world completely different from Earth, where I'm befriended by a group of elves and faced with the truth of magic.</p> <p>All the while, I'm honoring my promise to find the missing girl.</p> <p>Love and adventure await me in this strange realm where powerful magic and beautiful women abound. I just have to survive long enough to enjoy them.</p>"; 
